{"tid":1535044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"花冇百日紅，發夢吸精大法","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:58:12.000Z","uid":317188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b7280ad07854dade8fdd4508f238043b3b48dbd8","tid":1535044,"uid":317188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"全球咁多個國家，一定有大大小小示威，我地每一個星期仿照一個國家，再對仿照地區進行文宣，當藍絲反駁抹黑，我地順手燒理仿照地區，將當年時事同而家強連，目的持續下去，連帶更多人<br />\n先仿照其他國家和平手法成功，比佢地明白我地面對政治冷暴力，引支持，同時為日後合理化，同情化，以免失去支持，當仿照久，開始學下其他國家（你懂得？）"},{"pid":"f30fa3eba142b8dc39e105849118736b06b82f99","tid":1535044,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae473b813e3610a42ec82df3aedef44294da34c","tid":1535044,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\